817
00:57:35,535 --> 00:57:37,371
People call it a good choice

818
00:57:37,454 --> 00:57:39,331
or a correct answer.

819
00:57:40,916 --> 00:57:42,000
I'm 20.

820
00:57:43,293 --> 00:57:45,837
I'm still confused about values of life.

821
00:57:50,425 --> 00:57:52,135
If the coin comes up heads,

822
00:57:53,387 --> 00:57:55,597
I'll become a person you want me to be.

823
00:57:57,766 --> 00:57:59,434
If it comes up tails,

824
00:58:00,894 --> 00:58:02,604
You'll end up crying, Mom.

825
00:58:26,586 --> 00:58:28,714
Did the coin come up heads

826
00:58:29,047 --> 00:58:30,424
or tails?

