00:58:32,801 --> 00:58:34,177
Flipping the coin,

828
00:58:35,178 --> 00:58:37,014
which one did I wish for?

829
00:58:41,101 --> 00:58:43,228
I decided to call it tails.

830
00:59:33,862 --> 00:59:38,033
DANBAM

831
01:00:04,267 --> 01:00:06,394
I realize something as soon as I see him.

832
01:00:12,818 --> 01:00:15,320
Did you go home well last night?

833
01:00:16,696 --> 01:00:18,698
I didn't even need to hesitate.

834
01:00:20,909 --> 01:00:21,868
Yes.

835
01:00:26,331 --> 01:00:27,582
What brings you here?

836
01:00:45,976 --> 01:00:47,727
I want to be with you.

837
01:00:51,273 --> 01:00:52,816
What did you say?

838
01:00:54,151 --> 01:00:55,527
Like Mom said,

839
01:00:55,902 --> 01:00:57,612
I'm just too good.

840
01:00:59,781 --> 01:01:01,908
Love and success.

841
01:01:03,118 --> 01:01:04,703
I can achieve all those things.

842
01:01:07,914 --> 01:01:08,999
I mean...

843
01:01:10,041 --> 01:01:12,335
Feel sad just for a little while, Mom.

844
01:01:15,005 --> 01:01:18,091
I want to work here.

845
01:01:23,972 --> 01:01:27,517
I will help you achieve your dream, Boss.

846
01:01:31,396 --> 01:01:33,231
He's not just a mediocre man.

847
01:01:34,274 --> 01:01:36,276
I will turn him into someone amazing.

848
01:01:39,446 --> 01:01:40,447
I will.

849
01:01:52,876 --> 01:01:59,132
DANBAM

850
01:02:30,830 --> 01:02:34,167
